      "Text": "Security update for gimp",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for gimp fixes the following issues:\n\nChanges in gimp:\n\n- CVE-2026-58379: Fix PSP File Parsing Heap Buffer Overflow (bsc#1270299)\n- CVE-2026-58380: Fix buffer overflow in pnmscanner_gettoken (bsc#1270444)\n- CVE-2026-58381: Prevent double-freeing PSP layer name (bsc#1270239)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
